 "title": "Mistaken Identity",
 "summary": "In the main hangar of the entertainment ship Angry Rancor, the flamboyant Ka strides off the turbolift to find the self-styled pirate Shiari Vane in a heated standoff with a heavily armored bounty hunter, complete with a menacing Trandoshan enforcer at Vane's side. The easygoing Cataleya greets the scene casually, offering help while quietly arming herself from a locker, and Ka'una's interjection defuses the confrontation. The frustrated bounty hunter backs off with a threat, and Vane crows after him, loudly proclaiming herself the greatest pirate in the outer rim in a thoroughly comedic mix-up.",
